  <section class="ftco-section ftco-wrap-about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-7 d-flex">
          <div class="img img-1 mr-md-2" style="background-image: url(images/about.jpg);"></div>
          <div class="img img-2 ml-md-2" style="background-image: url(images/about-1.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 wrap-about pt-5 pt-md-5 pb-md-3 ftco-animate">
          <div class="heading-section mb-4 my-5 my-md-0">
            <span class="subheading">About</span>
            <h2 class="mb-4">DishCoveries</h2>
          </div>
          <p>DishCoveries is a virtual haven for culinary enthusiasts, aspiring chefs, and anyone with a passion for the art of cooking. We have created a vibrant online community that brings together a diverse range of individuals who share a common love for creating delectable dishes and exploring the world of flavors.

          </p><br>
          <p>
            At DishCoveries, we understand that cooking is not just a routine but an exciting journey of creativity and discovery. Whether you are a seasoned chef looking for inspiration or a home cook eager to learn new recipes, DishCoveries is here to nurture your culinary adventure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="ftco-section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 pb-2">
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center heading-section ftco-animate">
          <span class="subheading">Exploring</span>
          <h2 class="mb-4">DishCoveries</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate text-center">
          <div class="media block-6 services d-block">
            <div class="media-body p-2 mt-3">
              <h3 class="heading">Discover and Share Recipes</h3>
              <p>
                Users can find and share recipes easily. They can search for recipes based on ingredients, cuisines, or dietary preferences. Registered users can contribute their own recipes to the DishCoveries community.
              </p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate text-center">
          <div class="media block-6 services d-block">
            <div class="media-body p-2 mt-3">
              <h3 class="heading">Create Personalized Recipe Collections</h3>
              <p>DishCoveries lets users organize their favorite recipes. They can bookmark recipes, create themed collections (e.g., quick dinners, healthy desserts), and easily access their saved recipes whenever they log in.
              </p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate text-center">
          <div class="media block-6 services d-block">
            <div class="media-body p-2 mt-3">
              <h3 class="heading">Engage in a Cooking Community</h3>
              <p>
                DishCoveries is a platform for users to connect and share their love for cooking. It provides a space for users to share their cooking experiences and connect with fellow enthusiasts, fostering a vibrant community of cooking enthusiasts.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


